{"tid":1182473,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE娜璉刷新顏值新高度，仿佛化身歐洲中世紀貴族公主！","createTime":"2019-06-02T08:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T13:30:55.000Z","uid":74065,"like":11,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8940536c474427cbf9b1e13d5a6c1730da4cc7fd","tid":1182473,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T08:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_716072440fd90c707bb1922ee2a490c1/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-06-02/117187-740229.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_716072440fd90c707bb1922ee2a490c1%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-06-02%2F117187-740229.jpg&h=c23cd3bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n站姐給力，娜璉更給力~！<br />\n<br />\nTWICE在上週末5月25日和26日，以首爾場的演出打響世巡「TWICELIGHTS」的第一炮。 除了展示集體舞台表演，也準備了九人分為三組unit的特別舞台。 其中，娜璉在和定延、彩瑛、MINA一起cover《Born This Way》時的舞台造型可謂驚豔眾人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_b6c3d4cceeb84edb052d70d2a0daf8d0/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-06-02/117187-740233.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_b6c3d4cceeb84edb052d70d2a0daf8d0%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-06-02%2F117187-740233.jpg&h=03b7cba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n娜璉身穿的精緻珍珠鑽飾抹胸上下裝+choker的套裝盡顯雍容華貴又性感誘人的魅力，白色寬簷帽更是起到畫龍點睛的作用，這幅飯拍「傑作」在Twitter獲得2萬網友的點贊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_68beedc543f1ed43c7ed1d89ef5576db/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-06-02/117187-740235.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_68beedc543f1ed43c7ed1d89ef5576db%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-06-02%2F117187-740235.jpg&h=d014e555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外一套搭配身體鏈的白色連衣裙也彰顯了娜璉的嫵媚，特此附上。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_6599c4646d5d3246e873ede51f4a249b/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-06-02/117187-740228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_6599c4646d5d3246e873ede51f4a249b%2